Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:06.50,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(724.091,814.091)}The Chain-Link Stratagem
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:51.16,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(265.909,760.909)}Sūn Jiān\NStyled: "Wéntái"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Report! We've found a person in a well!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, they have found someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.92,0:01:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.43,0:02:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:16.83,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(212.727,756.818)}Huáng Gài\NStyled: "Gōngfù"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavens! My Lord, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:23.62,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(214.773,756.818)\fade(255,0,255,0,300,1790,2140)}Chéng Pǔ\NStyled: "Démóu"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's {\i1}the Heirloom Seal of the Realm!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Heirloom Seal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Of old, Biàn Hé, at the foot of Mount Jīngshān
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}saw a phoenix perching on a stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}He presented the stone to King Wén of Chǔ,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}he ordered it to be cracked open, finding a piece of jade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}It would be known as {\i1}the Jade of Hé!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Later, Qín Shǐ Huáng ordered his artisans to carve a seal from the jade,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}and Lǐ Sī engraved those eight characters on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Once, Qín Shǐ Huáng was patrolling Dòngtíng lake, and a violent storm erupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}The ship was about to sink so he threw the jade into the lake, the storm receded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Eight years later, when Shǐ Huáng was inspecting Huáyīn,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}a passerby presented him with the same seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Thus, the Jade Seal was returned to Qín.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}The next year, Qín Shǐ Huáng passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Eventually, his grandson, Ziyīng, would relinquish the jade Seal to Gāozǔ of Hàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Thereafter it has been known as the Heirloom Seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My lord, we can't stay here! We must hurry back to Jiāngdōng! Plan our next move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That is exactly what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, I will report sick, then leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:57.86,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(225,711.818)\fade(255,0,255,0,415,1581,1581)}Yuán Shào\NStyled: "Běnchū"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've caught a slight ailment, so I need to return to Chǎngshā.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to bid farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What illness? Could it be the illness of the Jade Seal!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you speak thus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We have risen against a traitor, to rid the empire of a menace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Seal belongs to the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, since you have it,\Nyou ought to return to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,After eliminating Dǒng Zhuō, will I return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you hide it and wish to scurry away!\NWhat is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That... how could the Heirloom Seal be within my possession?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the thing in the\N well near Jiànzhāng hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.72,0:04:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have it! Why interrogate me so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Return it now, or you will suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,By the high heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I indeed have the Seal and am hiding it for myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,May I meet a painful end, struck by arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Wéntái has made such an oath,\Nperhaps he doesn't have the Seal after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When you salvaged it, was this fellow present?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare deceive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Report! Sir, Cáo Cāo led his army to pursue Dǒng Zhuō.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He was ambushed and routed! He's now returning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder he's lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare a banquet behind the tent to solace Mèngdé!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:50.84,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(222.955,740.455)}Cáo Cāo\NStyled: "Mèngdé"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mèngdé.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mèngdé, don't be upset. \NVictory and defeat are all part of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}I fought for great justice, to rid the empire of a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}From eighteen directions, came armies fighting for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}My heart was grateful...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Utmost grateful...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}I was to have Běnchū rally the the people in Hénèi,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Lead them to Mèngjīn and Suānzǎo, guard Chénggāo,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:08:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}seize granaries, obstruct Huányuán, the great valley. Secure the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Gōnglù! You were to lead the men of Nányáng,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}garrison Dānxī, and enter Wǔ pass, so we could attack from three directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Thus, a high ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Not to fight, but to threaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Showing the realm our strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}the people would rebel, and thus pacify the land!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Yet, you hesitate and refuse to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}and we lost the world's hope in us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}For shame... For shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:46.82,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(310.909,756.818)\fade(255,0,255,0,550,1900,2300)}Gōngsūn Zàn\NStyled: "Bóguī"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,For shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:17.34,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Going through the Wormwood" ("蒿里行") \Nby Cáo Cāo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:21.44,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,925.364)}There rose men righteous in the east,\Nmarshaled legions to cruelty end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:27.80,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,925.364)}First they gathered in for Méngjīn, \Nfor their hearts that lied in Xiányáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:32.48,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,925.364)}Yet formations had divided,\N wavering like geese misguided,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:36.72,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,925.364)}Greed and weal drove them to contend, each would deal each a deadly end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:41.25,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,925.364)}Huáinán had a monarch made,\None in north carved a seal of jade
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:47.25,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Referring to Yuán Shù and Yuán Shào. Yuán Shù would declare himself Emperor, \NYuán Shào would attempt to make Liú Yú emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:45.35,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,925.364)}Lice and fleas infest worn armor, \Nfamilies ten thousands now dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:49.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,925.364)}Sun-blanched bones lie bare in fields,\Nno bird sings in a thousand lǐ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:52.18,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,925.364)}Of five score folks survives but one,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:55.76,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,925.364)}To reflect breaks the heart with sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen? Ministers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:22.86,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(237.273,726.136)\fade(255,0,255,0,575,5460,5740)}Dǒng Zhuō\NStyled: "Zhòngyǐng"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Those eighteen renegades are now in utter shambles, fragmented and split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They've already begun to eat each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now general Sūn Jiān is killed by the hands of Liú Biǎo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Qiáo Mào killed by Liú Dài!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hán Fù lost the Jì Province and fled to Zhāng Miǎo for shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And that Yuán Shào and Gōngsūn Zàn?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All willing to submit to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, you are all veteran ministers of the dynasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you remain loyal,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your old friend here can promise you prestige, rank, and wealth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, {\i1}Grand Preceptor{\i0}, for your great virtue!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring them in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Put them all to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I moved the capital and led you all here, I never got to feast with you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I shall be your host!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen? Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:46.54,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(216.818,746.591)\fade(255,0,255,0,575,3100,3500)}Wáng Yǔn\NStyled: "Zishī"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, no worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhāng Wēn conspired with Yuán Shù!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They planned to harm me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuán Shù snuck a letter for him, but by accident, my son, Fèngxiān,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,discovered it, and so he was executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, brother Běnchū?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You wench!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:52.94,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1198.636,726.136)\fade(255,0,255,0,350,3425,3860)}Diāochán
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sobbing and sighing late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:15:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you have an affair?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, how could I have an affair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If I may speak with honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Diāo Chán has received your generosity for sixteen years,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,teaching me to sing and dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Treating me with great kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I were crushed into dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it wouldn't be enough to repay a thousandth part of your kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I saw you anxious, instead of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I figure, there must be a great state affair worrying you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but I dare not ask too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I noticed that you broke down and refused to eat, nervous at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:17:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate myself for not being \Nable to ease your worries,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so I have been sighing \Nat the moon instead
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want you to notice, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, if you ever have a use for me,\NI will not back down even under threat of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could've thought the fate of\Nthe great Hàn Empire rests within your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you don't need to! \NThis is more than I will ever deserve!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, if you ever have a use for me,\NI will not back down, even after 10,000 deaths!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:19:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Right now, the people are in great peril.\NBoth the Emperor and his ministers are in jeopardy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.96,0:19:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}But it's not as if you cannot help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}The traitorous Dǒng Zhuō wants to usurp the throne!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}All officials of the court are unable to oppose him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Now Dǒng Zhuó has an adopted son by the name of Lǚ Bù.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}His power is extraordinary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}I have observed that both Dǒng Zhuó and Lǚ Bù are lecherous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}So I wish to employ a Chain-Link Stratagem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.11,0:19:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}First, I would let Lǚ Bù marry you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}and at the same time, present you to Dǒng Zhuō!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}If you can go in between them, you can strain the relationship between father and son!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Eventually, it will provoke Lǚ Bù to murder the traitor, and end a great evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}With that, it would restore the land once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Could you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}I already said it. Just give the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}I won't leave, even if it means death!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Sir, just do what you must, I know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If this discussion gets out, our family will be exterminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, don't grieve!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't repay your great kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:21:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,may I be cut to death by 10,000 knives!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I am beyond grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.09,0:21:50.60,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1202.727,769.091)}Lǚ Bù\NStyled: "Fèngxiān"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.87,0:22:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems you're in a good mood by yourself here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Excellency of the Masses{\i0}, its not often I see you in the hunting grounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you catch any game?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.15,0:22:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, no game.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,After I settled here, I often go out \Nwith my family to admire the nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you, sir, would like to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.45,0:22:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir, but the Grand Preceptor has orders for me. I dare not tardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.62,0:22:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do so, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.20,0:22:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do come visit me later on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.66,0:22:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.84,0:23:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not expect you to come! \NPlease excuse me for my discourtesy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.58,0:23:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me! Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.49,0:23:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, it's alright, it's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.14,0:23:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.23,0:23:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take the seat of honor, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.73,0:23:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.96,0:23:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you are a Ducal Minister,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I am just an officer! How could I accept?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.46,0:24:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You should take it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you must be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.11,0:24:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Within the realm today, many people claim to be heroes,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.58,0:24:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but only you, general, are worthy enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.75,0:24:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not honoring you because of your rank, but because of your abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.19,0:24:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But you, sir, refuse to claim the seat. \NCould it be that you look down on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.76,0:24:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! But if so, please allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.64,0:24:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.79,0:24:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall offer a cup for the Grand Preceptor, and for you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.36,0:24:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.90,0:25:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For the Grand Preceptor's longevity!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.88,0:25:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For the General's health! Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.61,0:25:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.18,0:25:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.69,0:26:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,General? General!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.32,0:26:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.43,0:26:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you seen General Lǚ before?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.83,0:26:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, who is this lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.20,0:26:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My humble daughter, Diāochán.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.37,0:26:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I pay my respects, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.61,0:26:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No need! No need!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.74,0:26:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,General, there's no need to be formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.38,0:26:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown us charity, and so I view you as part of my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.52,0:26:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, I told my daughter to come here so that she may see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.11,0:26:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My child, would you serve\N a cup for the General?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.19,0:27:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,General?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.86,0:27:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.01,0:27:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,General, even in my chamber,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.86,0:27:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've long heard of your reputation,\Nyour name echoes like thunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.01,0:27:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I look up to you, sir, I have made this cap\Nto express my admiration, just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.82,0:27:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It is just a token of my respect. \NI hope you do not laugh at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.53,0:27:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My lady, not only are you clever and deft,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.74,0:28:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but you are also very beautiful and pure! Your speech is elegant as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.01,0:28:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My lady, you may sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.79,0:28:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The General is a good friend.\NMy child, do take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.47,0:28:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.92,0:28:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,General,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.06,0:28:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to give you my\N daughter as a concubine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.06,0:28:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you will accept\N or refuse my offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.75,0:28:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that is the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.57,0:29:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I am at your complete service,\Nso that I may repay you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.55,0:29:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, we must set a date\N for an auspicious day
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.38,0:29:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring my daughter\N to the your residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.35,0:29:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Exalted father-in-law, I shall accept your generous gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.66,0:29:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to be so formal!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.97,0:29:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,General. General!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.60,0:29:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In the future, my family\N will rely on you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.94,0:29:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you are flattering me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.43,0:29:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's night already.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.18,0:30:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I intended for you to stay the night, \Nbut then Zhòngyǐng will grow suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.54,0:30:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's midnight already. \NI'll thank you another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.27,0:30:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I drank too much tonight, so I am not well.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.41,0:30:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon. I'll let my daughter accompany you, general.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.62,0:30:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as you please, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.52,0:31:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Court dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.01,0:31:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.00,0:31:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Fèngxiān!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.67,0:31:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to go {\i1}Méiwù{\i0}-manor to escort munitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.80,0:31:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I also need you to lead some troops to be garrisoned, just in case!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.84,0:31:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, please ease yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.35,0:32:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I will surely return within three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.15,0:32:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If I may dare, sir, can I ask you visit my humble abode for a banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.66,0:32:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How would you, sir, feel about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.13,0:32:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If the exalted Excellency of the Masses wants me to go, how could I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.04,0:32:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You flatter me! I am unworthy \Nof the Grand Preceptor's grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.23,0:32:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really have come! \NI present my humble respects!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.07,0:32:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.14,0:33:18.38,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Duke Wen of Zhou helped found the Zhou dynasty, considered the forefather of Confucian virtues.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.15,0:33:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, your majestic virtue towers over \NYī Yǐn and the Duke of Zhōu!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.36,0:33:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For you to have visited my humble abode gives me enough fortune to last three lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.44,0:33:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.20,0:33:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Preceptor,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.77,0:34:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,please drink a cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.10,0:34:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish the Grand Preceptor a prosperous life!\NYour virtue is enough to overflow the four seas!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.31,0:34:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.21,0:34:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.24,0:34:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}From a young age, I have studied astronomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.22,0:34:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Lately, I observed an odd phenomenon at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.55,0:34:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}and knew the days of the Hàn reign are waning.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.20,0:34:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Sir, your virtue echoes throughout the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.14,0:34:44.82,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Shùn, Yáo and Yǔ are the mythical rulers of the era of Three Sovereigns and Five Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.15,0:34:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}like Shùn succeeding Yáo and Yǔ succeeding Shùn
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.06,0:34:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}to finish their great cause, meet the hopes of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.14,0:34:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Sir, you can't disobey the will of heaven and the people!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.05,0:34:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}How could I dare do so?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.92,0:34:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Of old, those with principles fought those without it,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.90,0:35:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}those without virtue submitted to those with it. Sir, if you take over the realm,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.86,0:35:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}it would be in concert with the will of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.01,0:35:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}If the Mandate of Heaven is indeed mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.34,0:35:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}then you, gracious Ducal Excellency of the Masses, \Nare a founder of a new dynasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.44,0:35:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}I am most grateful for your support, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.56,0:35:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}I will never forget your great generosity, even in old age!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.28,0:35:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}Good! Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.55,0:35:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(705.682,879.545)}May I entertain you this once?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.19,0:35:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(707.727,879.545)}I have a dancer in my house. Would you be interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.90,0:35:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good, very good...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.88,0:38:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.12,0:38:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A singer, Diāo Chán.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.70,0:38:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent... she's excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.46,0:38:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Her dancing is perfect, and she is even more perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.05,0:38:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Serve a cup to the Preceptor!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.78,0:38:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.22,0:38:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How young are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.60,0:39:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am only sixteen years of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.30,0:39:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're truly a deity amongst fairies!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.24,0:39:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to present this woman to you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.14,0:39:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know whether you agree or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.38,0:39:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, since you've shown me so much kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.45,0:39:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,what can I do to repay you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.42,0:39:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.12,0:39:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,For her to be presented to you, sir, is a blessing!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.06,0:39:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You flatter me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.26,0:39:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gracious Ducal Minister, gifting this lovely beauty to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.62,0:39:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,shows your great virtue indeed! I am very grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.65,0:39:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You flatter me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.24,0:39:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to respect you, this is the least I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.51,0:39:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready my chariot!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.78,0:39:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's return home!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.59,0:39:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send my daughter to your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.97,0:40:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to escort further, my good sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.44,0:40:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do return.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.34,0:40:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Grand Preceptor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.73,0:40:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.53,0:40:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare to trick me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.54,0:40:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,General, this is no place to talk. We'll talk inside.
